data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. One or more photo(s) has been virtually staged. Welcome to this ready to move in townhome in the Broadway Centre community of Brandon! This corner lot property offers unique features such as a retractable screened in garage with custom flooring, vaulted ceilings, an upstairs loft area, screened lanai, high-end water filtration system and close proximity to neighborhood guest parking. As you enter through the proper foyer, you are greeted by a large kitchen that offers a full appliance suite, stone countertops, convenient access to the laundry room, and a breakfast bar. Continue into the open concept great room, dining room combo with impressive vaulted ceilings and lots of light from the generous amount of windows. The first floor is equipped with a half bathroom, perfect for guests, and downstairs primary suite, offering ease and convenience. The large primary suite features his and hers closets, a sizable double vanity, linen closet, and step in shower. As you make your way up the staircase, you'll be greeted by an upstairs loft area, perfect for an office, play room, or media room. On the second floor, you'll find two spacious bedrooms in addition to a full bathroom and linen closet. Enjoy the beautiful Florida weather in the garage with a custom made retractable screen and epoxied floors, or in the screened in covered lanai overlooking a bit of green space which offers a sense of serenity while enjoying your morning coffee. This neighborhood also offers a community pool.  This location is close to I75 and I4 which offers a quick commute into Tampa or East to Lakeland and Orlando.
